howItWorks: |
  <h2>How this topsoil calculator works</h2>
  <p>The calculator multiplies area by depth to estimate topsoil volume. It then converts cubic feet to cubic yards and estimates the number of bags if you are buying bagged topsoil.</p>
  <h2>Common topsoil depths</h2>
  <p>A thin lawn topdressing may use less than an inch. New garden beds, grading, and low-spot filling may need several inches depending on the project.</p>
